        'b93 v1.7.67 — Phase 2 S3 PARITY HARDENING (S3.1e/f/g + IP-CB). Bundles four post-b92 patches that were live on PM2 since 2026-04-26 but unversioned. (S3.1e) serverBrain._computeFusionParity is a shadow-pure path used only by _runShadowCycle; bypasses the live-fusion modifier stack (structure, liquidity, journal, knn, session, volatility, tilt, trapRisk, regimeDanger) so parity rows reflect pure decision logic, not modifier drift; database.queryParityReport split into PRIMARY vs COVERAGE with adjusted-agreement metric (NO_TRADE/NO_TRADE counted as match regardless of dir) plus per-user breakdown. (S3.1f) marketFeed aggTrade listener fix restores serverOrderflow.getFlow() — pre-fix returned buyVol=0/sellVol=0 universally, post-fix OFI is present on 100% of server-side parity rows across BNB/BTC/ETH/SOL. (S3.1g) client autotrade.ts moves FUSION_CACHE+PRIMARY parity POST earlier in runAutoTradeCheck, before EXEC_LOCKED/DATA_STALL/_isExecAllowed/KILL gates; multi-sym COVERAGE emit unchanged; placeAutoTrade/DSL/Risk Rails/exchange execution paths untouched; restored BTC PRIMARY paired sample from <2/h trickle to 7158 over 24h. (IP-CB) binanceSigner adds process-global IP-level circuit breaker for 418/429: parses "banned until <ts>" from Binance error messages, falls back to 60s cooldown when timestamp absent; per-user CB does not protect against IP-scope bans because Binance enforces 418/429 per IP not per API key — without IP-CB any user retries extend the global ban. T+24h S3.1g GREEN: PRIMARY paired 7158 (gate ≥500), adjusted agreement 100.0% (gate ≥95%), decision agreement 100.0%, real mismatches 0, OFI sanity 100% on all 4 alts, runtime errors 0, no induced /api/place-order calls. T+72h soak (Wed 2026-04-29 11:01 UTC) remains queued as post-promotion confirmation only; operator-promoted S3 to GREEN on T+24h evidence. SERVER_BRAIN=false and SERVER_AT=false unchanged; no live decision flip. S4 (Bybit live-entry parity) remains BLOCKED until explicit operator GO; bybitSigner.js still does not exist. S5–S12 remain BLOCKED behind their own gates. Post-S3 bug fixes (28 known) remain DEFERRED. Files: server/services/serverBrain.js, server/services/marketFeed.js, server/services/database.js, server/services/binanceSigner.js, client/src/trading/autotrade.ts, server/version.js. Backups: *.bak.s31e, *.bak.s31f, *.bak.s31g, *.bak.ip-cb. Tests: node --check clean on all 4 server files, client tsc --noEmit clean, vite build clean (749ms, bundle index-BKhQaoiQ.js 1.74MB). Previous: b92 v1.7.66 — Phase 2 S3 PARITY HARNESS (shadow-only instrumentation).',
